question: 오늘 서울 Data cei 알려줘
query: SELECT dt, hh, '5G' as nw, city_name, data_cfi, data_cei     FROM o_tpani_cem5g.city_1h    WHERE dt = DATE_FORMAT(CURRENT_DATE, '%Y%m%d')    AND city_name = '서울'UNION ALLSELECT dt, hh, 'LTE' as nw, city_name, data_cfi, data_cei     FROM o_tpani_cem.city_1h    WHERE dt = DATE_FORMAT(CURRENT_DATE, '%Y%m%d')    AND city_name = '서울'ORDER BY hh asc

question: 중부Infra 시도별 CEI 보여 줘
query: SELECT dt, '5G' as nw, city_name, hdv_cfi, data_cfi, hdv_cei, data_cei FROM o_tpani_cem5g.city_1dWHERE dt = REPLACE(CAST(date_add('day', -1, current_date) AS varchar), '-', '')AND city_name in ('강원', '충북', '충남', '대전', '세종')UNION ALL SELECT dt, 'LTE' as nw, city_name, hdv_cfi, data_cfi, hdv_cei, data_cei FROM o_tpani_cem.city_1dWHERE dt = REPLACE(CAST(date_add('day', -1, current_date) AS varchar), '-', '')AND city_name in ('강원', '충북', '충남', '대전', '세종')

question: o_tpani_cem.cell_1h 테이블에서 24년 5월 28일 13시~17시 수내1동에서 Data 사용자수가 많았던 쎌 5개 조회해줘
query: SELECT     dt,     dong_name,    enb_name,    cell_id,    data_user_cnt FROM o_tpani_cem.cell_1hWHERE dt='20240518' AND hh IN ('13', '14', '15', '16')  AND dong_name = '수내1동'ORDER BY data_user_cnt DESCLIMIT 5;

question: 2024년 5/18일 중부 Data 접속품질 접속지표가 가장 안좋았던 쎌 10개 찾아줘
query: SELECT   branch_id,  branch_name,  team_id,  team_name,  company_id,  company_name,  part_id,  part_name,  ems_id,  enb_cell_id,  enb_id,  enb_name,  cell_id,  data_com_access_qoe1_qos1FROM   o_tpani_cem.cell_1hWHERE   dt = '20240518' AND  branch_name = '{중부Infra}' AND data_com_access_qoe1_qos1>=0ORDER BY   data_com_access_qoe1_qos1 ASCLIMIT 10;

question: 수도권Infra 한 달 간 CEI 뽑아 줘
query: SELECT dt, '5G' as nw,     branch_name,     hdv_cfi, data_cfi, hdv_cei, data_cei FROM o_tpani_cem5g.bran_1d    WHERE dt >= REPLACE(CAST(date_add('day', -31, current_date) AS varchar), '-', '')    AND branch_name ='수도권Infra'UNION ALLSELECT dt, 'LTE' as nw,     branch_name,    hdv_cfi, data_cfi, hdv_cei, data_cei FROM o_tpani_cem.bran_1d    WHERE dt >= REPLACE(CAST(date_add('day', -31, current_date) AS varchar), '-', '')    AND branch_name ='수도권Infra'

question: 어제 강북Access Infra팀에서 Data CD 카운트가 가장 많은 기지국 10개 알려줘
query: SELECT dt, enb_id , enb_name, team_name , SUM(data_cd_count) AS data_cd_count FROM (SELECT dt, enb_id , enb_name, team_name , data_cfi_access_drop_cnt  as data_cd_count    FROM o_tpani_cem5g.enb_mno_1d    WHERE dt = DATE_FORMAT(DATE_ADD('day', -1, CURRENT_DATE), '%Y%m%d')     AND team_name = '강북Access Infra팀'    AND mno_code = '1'UNION ALLSELECT dt, enb_id , enb_name, team_name , data_cfi_access_drop_cnt  as data_cd_count    FROM o_tpani_cem.enb_1d    WHERE dt = DATE_FORMAT(DATE_ADD('day', -1, CURRENT_DATE), '%Y%m%d')     AND team_name = '강북Access Infra팀')GROUP BY dt, enb_id, enb_name, team_nameORDER BY data_cd_count DESC LIMIT 10

question: 강북Access Infra팀 CEI 데이터를 오늘, 어제, 전주 데이터를 시간 단위로 뽑아 줘
query: SELECT dt, hh, '5G' as nw, team_name, hdv_cfi, data_cfi, hdv_cei, data_cei FROM o_tpani_cem5g.team_1hWHERE dt in (REPLACE(CAST(date_add('day', 0, current_date) AS varchar), '-', ''), REPLACE(CAST(date_add('day', -1, current_date) AS varchar), '-', ''), REPLACE(CAST(date_add('day', -7, current_date) AS varchar), '-', ''))AND team_name in ('강북Access Infra팀')UNION ALLSELECT dt, hh, 'LTE' as nw, team_name, hdv_cfi, data_cfi, hdv_cei, data_cei FROM o_tpani_cem.team_1hWHERE dt in (REPLACE(CAST(date_add('day', 0, current_date) AS varchar), '-', ''), REPLACE(CAST(date_add('day', -1, current_date) AS varchar), '-', ''), REPLACE(CAST(date_add('day', -7, current_date) AS varchar), '-', ''))AND team_name in ('강북Access Infra팀')

question: 금천구 HDV CD 제일 많이 발생한 셀 알려 줘
query: SELECT dt, nw, gu_name, enb_id, cell_id, hdv_com_drop_cnt FROM (  SELECT dt, '5G' as nw, gu_name, enb_id, cell_id, hdv_com_drop_cnt FROM o_tpani_cem5g.cell_mno_1d      WHERE dt =REPLACE(CAST(date_add('day', -1, current_date) AS varchar), '-', '')      AND mno_code ='1'      AND gu_name='금천구'  UNION ALL   SELECT dt, 'LTE' as nw, gu_name, enb_id, cell_id, hdv_com_drop_cnt FROM o_tpani_cem.cell_1d      WHERE dt =REPLACE(CAST(date_add('day', -1, current_date) AS varchar), '-', '')      AND gu_name='금천구')ORDER BY hdv_com_drop_cnt DESC LIMIT 1;

question: 아이폰 13 계열의 CEI 알려 줘
